Features: of aim_extreme

- High-Detail terrian that surpasses any aim map in modern society!

- Water effects rendered by the source engine.

- High-Detail buildings to give the feel of battle. 

- An all-new approach to what aim should be like. 

- Sounds that play the real-like feel.

Download Description:

This map for counter-strike source promises to go beyond the visuals 
and gameplay of ANY aim map as of today! Utilizing the revolutonary graphics 
engine, this map boast visuals unlike any other in its class! Guarenteed!

Map supports 32 player, NO BOT SUPPORT!.
Works on server.
